---
description: Submodule ownership and two-step commits
alwaysApply: true
---

- Edit API/UI/bot code inside the matching submodule directory.
- Open PRs against the component repo, not the platform, for component work.
- After a component merge, bump the submodule SHA in the platform with a message like `Bump xastrinxop-ui submodule`.
- Follow CONTRIBUTING.md.
